title: Pennsylvania Democratic Party
deleted: Democrats made significant gains in voter registration during the [[2008 United States presidential election|2008 Presidential election]], with registered Democrats now outnumbering registered Republicans almost by a 3-2 margin.<ref>http://www.philly.com/philly/hp/news_update/20081017_Pa__Democrats_now_outnumber_GOP_by_almost_1_2_million.html</ref> Democrats now outnumber Republicans in the state of Pennsylvania by 1.2 million voters.
